// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0

pragma solidity >=0.7.0 <0.9.0;
contract Greeter
{
    string public greeting;
    constructor()
    {
        greeting = "Hello";
    }
    function setGreeting(string memory _greeting) public
    {
        greeting = _greeting;
    }
    function greet() view public returns (string memory)
    {
        return greeting;
    }
}
